message.body: I'm happy you guys didn't forget about me. :p
By the way, I won't be able to get back to Philly until January.
No never!!! January OK fine we will have to wait until then. Best of luck bud. I know you can make it work. What part of Baltimore are you in?
I'm used to be near Hollins markets in Southwest Baltimore. It's in the ghetto and I got tired of kids messing with my car, so I moved near downtown.
I'm right next to the Meyerhoff Symphony Hall, if you know about that.
